                    11+ years of engineering expertise, accelerated by modern
                    tools. Production-ready systems with proper architecture,
                    security, and testing.
                </p>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-8">
                    <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-cyan-400"
                        >$5,000-12,000</span
                    >
                    <span class="text-gray-600">|</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-400">3 Tiers Available</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-600">|</span>
                    <span class="text-gray-400">50% Upfront</span>
                </div>
                <a
                    href="/"
                    class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-cyan-400 hover:text-cyan-300 transition font-medium"
                >
                    View all pricing tiers
